Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:12.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就沒有什麼能把高木同學嚇得尖叫的辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:19.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之 像這樣每天都被她捉弄的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:22.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:28.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:30.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:36.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:41.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起去學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:44.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比身高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剛才被她看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要一起騎車去學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:34.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被發現的話會挨罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是不好意思才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:42.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:47.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看來我撞上電線杆的事情沒被她看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:54.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片也終於換長袖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最近變冷了 感覺差不多該換了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你長個了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:09.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,春天的時候感覺你的制服比現在寬鬆一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:16.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在有種「制服 is 正義」的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道我到發育期了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:27.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 最近一個勁地長個子 真難辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道到了發育期嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:33.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學倒是沒感覺有什麼變化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:40.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你這可是性騷擾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,居然說沒變化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不是這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說的是身高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在說身高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你以為我在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:15.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺你還是沒怎麼長高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:18.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不不 長高了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:22.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說不定我現在比高木同學還要高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那來比比身高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要來這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,穿著鞋子比不出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,小心遲到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來 背對背站好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺好暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:10.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一般不都是輪流貼著牆壁作記號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:12.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,兩個人背對著量更準嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,應該差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來嘛 西片也來確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我沒說錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你沒墊腳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 你居然懷疑我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:42.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:50.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,面對面的話 就算墊腳也會知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:55.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個 那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:08.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺好像我要高一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為我剛才墊腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然墊腳了啊 大騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可沒有說過我沒墊腳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 終於贏過我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個高木同學 一副從容的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心裡肯定很不甘心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有 我沒有不甘心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:36.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為要是塊頭變大的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:38.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就會撞上電線杆 很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看到了嗎 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,走吧 去學校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 高木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:09.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有那麼冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉很怕冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 你手好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怕冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:31.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再這樣干我可饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們的手為什麼那麼冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:46.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手冷的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,內心很溫暖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:56.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得內心很溫暖的人不會做剛才那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:08:00.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了好了 別那麼記仇嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你再幹的話我真的要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你明明已經生氣了好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:12.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 不要啊早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是心暖攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,救命啊 由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是剛才的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉的手 好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但她的心拔涼拔涼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊 不要靠過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心寒攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:40.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,走為上策
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:41.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:42.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:45.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你也可以摸回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:59.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好冷啊好冷啊 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:06.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能會這樣幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:13.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都叫你住手了 好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:18.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手冷的人 內心是暖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪裡暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:25.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木和西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:27.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天一起上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,關係真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:33.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他們果然在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:44.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片和高木在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:45.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他們關係特別好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉 你很羨慕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 因為嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,與其說是羨慕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:02.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 由加莉說想和男生唧唧我我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才沒這樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要突然跟我搭話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,本來快要尿出來的 現在尿不出來了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:18.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個很有趣的 去看看比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 我會看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:32.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想到了很厲害的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,如果是這個犀利的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:37.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放學的時候肯定能捉弄到高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在偷笑什麼呢 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好猥瑣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才沒有想那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那種事情是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你臉好紅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:57.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我走著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:13.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 難道她發覺我在設計她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你要再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:22.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放學時你說不定還會改變主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:31.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以的話到時候再給我答覆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她究竟怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了 反正不被發覺就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天來我家玩超級大亂鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7}原文スパプラ，應該是山寨明星大亂?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:49.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 又要陪女朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:57.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是高木同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哈？你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,根本就不是那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木和西片沒在交往哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我剛才在廁所聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:11.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:12.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,突然想去小便了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,廁所…廁所…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:22.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那傢伙剛才在廁所幹什麼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然你們沒在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那為什麼你會和高木同學一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛 因為被她邀請了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:36.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這不就是因為在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,應該不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下節課要去實驗室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 趕緊走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:13:01.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我覺得高木同學只是想捉弄我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天不可以繞遠路了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:14.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想吃椪柑冰棍 我想吃椪柑冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大冷天的還吃什麼冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在被爐吃冰棍超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:19.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「給我答覆」也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:27.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要我重新邀請她的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺有點不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還沒邀請過她一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 高木同學來問我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只要說個Yes就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:49.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天有人問我是不是在和西片交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:55.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後 我好像被認為是喜歡西片的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:14:00.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是不是因為總是我在邀請你一起回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來這就是你的目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,創造出讓我來邀請你的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:13.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後取笑我害羞的反應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要強裝平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「哼 這樣啊」這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:25.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:26.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:31.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 關於早上的答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:38.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正我沒什麼事 一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加油啊我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要跨過了這一關
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就能捉弄到高木同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:57.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起回家怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:18.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片好像還有什麼計劃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:30.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然暴露了 那還是不要做比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但我好不容易想出來的點子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:38.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說我還完全沒想過要怎樣弄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:45.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要不要買果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:48.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺喉嚨乾乾的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大部分都賣完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明想喝冷飲的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剩下的只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,紅豆湯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有獵奇的飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.65,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\pos(918,330)\frz3.238}艾草汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.65,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs50\pos(1164,702)}西瓜味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺無論選哪個都會後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,無論選哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:16.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要去別的自動販賣機看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:21.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我喉嚨也渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之先…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:32.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好難喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:35.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看包裝就能猜到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,錢白花了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:40.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣一來就能開始我的計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:52.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好喝的熱飲和難喝得要命的飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:54.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二選一問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:08.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好喝但是燙手的飲料和難喝得要命的飲料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:12.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難以選擇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你就犯難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:17.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓我看看你為難的表情 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:18.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:23.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是我喝了好喝的熱飲發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片會來探望我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:30.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這有什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,關係大著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:42.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我應該會去探望你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我選好喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:51.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:57.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學完全沒有為難嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:02.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不如說為難的是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二選一問題的作戰失敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不 放棄還為之過早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那下一題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:16.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是選一輩子沒有零花錢呢 還是不再捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一輩子沒有零花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:19.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:24.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為我有壓歲錢作積蓄 暫時沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到了高中只要打工就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:30.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以還是選捉弄西片比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我太小瞧高木同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得問些更刁鑽的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,從剛才開始你就在問些奇怪的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:44.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說 你想讓我為難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒 沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我也要提問了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:58.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不在和被我捉弄一輩子 哪個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不在是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:03.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:09.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然我也不想被她捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:13.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但消失什麼的…那也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那 我選被你捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然喜歡被捉弄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有 肯定是討厭被捉弄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:29.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不太希望你消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說 你想一輩子和我在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:35.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你臉好紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓我發窘就這麼有意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也得問個好問題才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:46.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼下一題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:48.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 還要繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:54.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一輩子考零分 以及和我接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:58.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接…接…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:06.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,考零分 看了書也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:08.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 無論幹什麼都是零分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:14.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣的話不僅以後肯定拿不到零花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚至連高中也上不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:20.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但要選了接吻的話 肯定會被她捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你很糾結嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我越糾結 高木同學她就越開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得趕緊作出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,零分太殘酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那 那就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,選不是考零分那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是考零分的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接 接吻的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:11.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:14.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片的個子要高一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:17.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了西片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在比身高而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:36.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到頭來又被狠狠地捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我學到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:43.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其中一個選項一定要是選不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:46.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要另一個是捉弄用的選項
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這場對決就能穩贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:50.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 下一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:57.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,倒立著繞校園走一圈和兩個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:59.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,稍微等一下 我不會倒立
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:02.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說還輪不到我提問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,首先要回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:05.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 你看…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:50.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:54.95,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:01:05.25,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:14.09,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:22.35,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.31,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:30.69,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:34.61,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:38.49,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:46.62,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:54.88,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:02:00.30,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
