Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:16.14,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}想把這遼闊宇宙中絕無僅有的小小的相思之情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:25.11,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}傳達給蔚藍地球上廣闊世界中小小島嶼上的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:31.16,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}與你邂逅 光陰飛逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:35.83,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}飽含思念的信件堆積如山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:40.75,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不知不覺我們心生共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:45.46,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}時而充滿激情 時而傷感不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:50.14,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}迴響漸漸遠去 到那遙遠彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:54.89,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那溫柔的歌聲 改變了我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:01.69,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你看 對你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:07.69,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}重要的人近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:13.83,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}只願你能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.20,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}這響徹天地的戀歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:26.17,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你聽 你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:31.51,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}聽見了嗎
